      <title>消息人士称，英国监管机构正在考虑进一步放宽银行家奖金规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-watchdogs-weigh-further-easing-banker-bonus-rules-sources-say-2024-10-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消息人士周三称，​​英国最高金融监管机构正准备就危机时期延期奖金和追回款规则的改革展开磋商，他们正在考虑另一项可能提高英国银行业的竞争力的规则改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-watchdogs-weigh-further-easing-banker-bonus-rules-sources-say-2024-10-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 16:48:34 GMT</pubDate>
