      <title>米尔顿威胁要颠覆佛罗里达州不稳定的房主保险市场</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/milton-threatens-upend-shaky-florida-homeowners-insurance-market-2024-10-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风米尔顿有可能淹没佛罗里达州陷入困境的财产保险市场，可能推高保险价格并威胁到这个风暴多发地区的保险覆盖范围，而该地区的保险成本已经是全美最高的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/milton-threatens-upend-shaky-florida-homeowners-insurance-market-2024-10-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 16:48:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
